Telescope; scope_park; Park the telescope
Telescope; scope_unpark; Unpark the telescope
Telescope; scope_position; Show the telescope position
Telescope; scope_alignment; Make a telescope pointing model
Telescope; eqmod_alignment; Make a Eqmod telescope pointing model
Filter; focuser_position_per_filter; Setting focuser position per filters, version 2025-11-15
Preprocessing; siril.pkg; Preprocessing scripts for Bias,Dark,Flat,Light using Siril (require to install Siril)
Spectroscope; UVEX4.pkg; Scripts for the UVEX4 spectroscope using both Alpaca and serial link
Spectroscope; Spectro_SetGuideMethod; Allow to define per target guiding strategy and parameters
Spectroscope; specinti.pkg; Process spectra with specINTI
Spectroscope; aod.script; Get the Aerosol Optical Depth from Copernicus, add it to FITS header
Calibrator; cover_open; Open the telescope cover
Calibrator; cover_close; Close the telescope cover
Calibrator; calibrator_on; Turn the calibrator light on
Calibrator; calibrator_off; Turn the calibrator light off
Initialization; startup; Startup action when CCDciel is started
Initialization; shutdown; Close action when CCDciel is exited
Computer; computer_shutdown; Shutdown the computer
Computer; computer_to_sleep; Make the computer to sleep
